<p>This visual guide to <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/book/view/684">Half-Life Sprites</a> provides a quick view of 128 images in the Sprite folder of the Pak0.pak file.<br> <br>
Sprites can add <i>Impact</i> to the atmosphere of an otherwise dull scene. So next time you need one, look no further...</p>
